sequenceDiagram
    participant Dev as 开发者
    participant NPM as npm / package.json
    participant Vite as Vite 构建系统
    participant FS as 文件系统
    participant Browser as 浏览器/APP

    Note over Dev,Browser: Web 开发流程 (npm run dev:web)
    Dev->>NPM: npm run dev:web
    NPM->>Vite: vite --config vite.config.web.js
    Vite->>FS: 读取 vite.config.web.js (VITE_PLATFORM=web)
    Vite->>FS: 读取 src/web/index.html
    Vite->>FS: 解析 src/web/main.jsx
    Vite->>FS: 解析 src/web/App.jsx
    Vite->>FS: import shared/api/* (VITE_API_BASE=/api)
    Vite->>FS: import shared/contexts/AuthContext
    Vite->>FS: import shared/components/*
    Vite->>FS: import web/components/Navbar
    Vite->>FS: import web/components/Footer
    Vite->>FS: import web/pages/*
    Vite-->>Browser: 启动 dev server (:3000)

    Note over Dev,Browser: APP 开发流程 (npm run dev:app)
    Dev->>NPM: npm run dev:app
    NPM->>Vite: vite --config vite.config.app.js
    Vite->>FS: 读取 vite.config.app.js (VITE_PLATFORM=app)
    Vite->>FS: 读取 src/app/index.html
    Vite->>FS: 解析 src/app/main.jsx
    Vite->>FS: 解析 src/app/App.jsx
    Vite->>FS: import shared/api/* (VITE_API_BASE=/api)
    Vite->>FS: import shared/contexts/AuthContext
    Vite->>FS: import shared/components/*
    Vite->>FS: import app/components/Navbar
    Vite->>FS: import app/pages/*
    Note over Vite: app/App.jsx 含 Capacitor 动态导入
    Vite-->>Browser: 启动 dev server (:3000)

    Note over Dev,Browser: Web 构建流程 (npm run build:web)
    Dev->>NPM: npm run build:web
    NPM->>Vite: vite build --config vite.config.web.js
    Vite->>FS: 编译 src/web/ 入口
    Vite->>FS: 打包 shared/ 依赖
    Vite->>FS: 输出到 dist/web/
    Note over Vite: 产物不含 Capacitor 代码

    Note over Dev,Browser: APP 构建流程 (npm run build:app)
    Dev->>NPM: npm run build:app
    NPM->>Vite: vite build --config vite.config.app.js
    Vite->>FS: 编译 src/app/ 入口
    Vite->>FS: 打包 shared/ 依赖
    Vite->>FS: 输出到 dist/app/
    Note over Vite: 产物含 Capacitor 代码
